<h1>Typesetting</h1>

<p>
        I offer typesetting services for things like papers, articles, or any other short to mid length literature. If you are interested in having your document typeset please contact me. My typesetting offers:
        
        <ol>
                <li>Versatile styling. I can do any number of styles from modern to Victorian.</li>
                <li>Consistent, professional formatting. Your document will always have perfectly consistent formatting.</li>
                <li>Powerful typesetting. I can include graphs, tables, flowcharts, images, and math.</li>
                <li>Publication quality graphics. I can create everything from mind maps to automata and circuit diagrams.</li>
                <li>Total cross platform compatibility. My final product ships as a PDF file, meaning there is no variance between devices.</li>
                <li>Embedded styling. All fonts and formatting are embedded, ensuring that no matter who views the document it will maintain consistency.</li>
                <li>Perfect printing. I can typeset your document for any standard size paper (including legal) so that it will always print true.</li>
        </ol>
</p>

<h2>Pricing</h2>

<p>Pricing is very variable depending on the job in question. A simple essay would cost arround $10, and more complicated work that includes graphics would cost more.</p>
